  <abstract>
    <p>
      This is a textbook for teaching a first introduction to data science.
      We define <term>data science</term> as the process of generating insight from data
      through <term>reproducible</term> and <term>auditable</term> processes.
      In this book, you will learn how to identify common problems in data science
      and solve those problems with reproducible and auditable workflows using the
      R programming language.
    </p>
  </abstract>

